Package clientGUI

Class ApproveCustomersGUIController

  • java.lang.Object
    • clientGUI.ApproveCustomersGUIController
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.fxml.Initializable
    public class ApproveCustomersGUIController
extends java.lang.Object
implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
    ApproveCustomersGUIController class is responsible for allowing each shop manager to approve customers, by giving them username and password, and clicking approve customer button they will be recognized in the system and login to their accounts.

    Project Name: Zer-Li (Flowers store in Java)

    Version:
    V1.00 2022
    Author:
    Habib Ibrahim, Vitaly Rofman, Ibrahim Daoud, Yosif Hosen
